      "resourcesVsBenefits": "Eleven programs provide financial benefits based on income, assets, or care needs — like Medicaid waivers that pay for home care or LIHEAP that covers utility bills. Five programs offer free resources to all seniors regardless of income: Medicare counseling through SHIP, legal services, nursing home advocacy, job training for those 55+, and prescription drug assistance. Your parent can access free resources immediately while you work on benefit applications."
