            "text": "PACE is NOT available statewide. Only specific counties in Northwest Arkansas (Benton, Madison, Washington) and Northeast Arkansas (Craighead, Cross, Greene, Lawrence, Mississippi, Poinsett, Randolph) are served. Check your parent's address before applying."
